column2: "This is Deegnacht... Wow, it really is completely different from Diggnutt."
"What? Oh, sure. I can tell just by looking. Of course, this is the first time I've ever actually seen one with my own eyeballs."
"Anyway, here's your reward. Now, to carve it up while it's still fresh. Looks like Deegnacht carpaccio will be on today's menu!"
